First Department,

June, 1948.

(June 1, 1948.) American Cities Power and Light Corporation et al., Appellants, v. Harrison Williams, Respondent, et al., Defendants.

Judgment and order unanimously affirmed, with, costs. No opinion. Present — Glennon, J. P., Dore, Cohn, Callahan and Van Voorhis, JJ. [See post, p. 876.]
